LVDS-1#1 Warning
Bidirection LVDS IOs  
The following port(s) use the LVDS_25 I/O standard and have bi-directional differential usage. Please note that LVDS_25 is a fixed impedance structure optimized to 100ohm differential. This is only intended to be used in point-to-point transmissions that do not have turn around timing requirements. If the intended usage is a bus structure, please use BLVDS/BLVDS_25, instead. ext_clk_i_n_0, ext_clk_i_p_0, generator_lvds_clk_n_0, generator_lvds_clk_p_0, generator_lvds_data_n_0, generator_lvds_data_p_0, generator_lvds_valid_n_0, generator_lvds_valid_p_0, lvds_n_i_0, lvds_p_i_0, valid_n_i_0, valid_p_i_0.
